name: "The Butcher", see info (Gottiline/Razors Edge)...V
description:
***(1) ATTEMPT: STUD ONLY, DETAILS DISCUSSED VIA CONTACT***
THE BUTCHER IS A LARGE  BLACK & WHITE AMERICAN PIT BULL MALE, WHO BY NATURE, IS MORE THAN WILLING WHEN IT COMES TO BREEDING TIME!  HOWEVER, HE'S A UKC CERTIFIED PURPLE RIBBON BRED "HIGHCLASS" PIT AND HAS A LONG BLOOD LINE OF WELL KNOWN "BIG DOGS" BEFORE HIM & WE CHOOSE TO KEEP THAT STRONG BLOOD LINE GOING.  HE'S WELL TAKEN CARE OF BY DAD, MOM, & BROTHER...SO HE DOESN'T HAVE TIME TO STRUT THE NEIGHBORHOOD & CHASE JUST ANY LOOSE TAIL.
THE FEMALES HE'S TO BE BREED WITH, ARE HAND CHOSEN BY THE OWNERS. 
WE'LL TAKE ALL OF THE FOLLOWING INTO CONSIDERATION - HER PAPERS, BLOOD LINE, HEALTH, OUTCOME OF HER LAST PUPS, & LOOKS.  IF YOU THINK YOU MAY HAVE THAT SPECIAL BITCH FOR THE BUTCHER, NEAR OR FAR, CONTACT US VIA THE "CONTACT" PAGE FOR ANY INQUIRIES OR TO SEE IF WE CAN GET A "HOOK-UP" GOIN'.
NOTE: PRICE LISTED IS SUBJECT TO CHANGE DEPENDING ON AGREEMENT BETWEEN OWNERS.
